<subSubSection id="889E944E80F392CCCE741E0EC117E707" pageId="null" pageNumber="275" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="E5E4271A30BB0C098EC1AC0A53B680E1" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Silber-Wegerich</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="1AE4AE6FC28491625112E53440DA885A" pageId="null" pageNumber="275" type="description">
<paragraph id="C644846ECF7D47E6F6FFB47C6D0CB891" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="15690D121EA72279EB9DE23ACD2F5349" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Plantago" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="275" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lanceolata">
<emphasis id="5ED249285B7EBCCD077E37C1FEB54A1F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">P. lanceolata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 4) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="1EC6ED7C90C119AC52BF3DCF1FEA3077" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
Stiel der 
<normalizedToken id="3B884D38099C735072D7B0F6343D1DD9" originalValue="Blütenähre" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Bluetenaehre</normalizedToken>
unter der 
<normalizedToken id="3174A08088AEB0AEC14C6531418E10DF" originalValue="Ähre" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Aehre</normalizedToken>
mit zahlreichen, wenig tiefen Rillen; 
<normalizedToken id="AAB772C4799BBEF3DF88782B1CE492F8" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
beiderseits dicht anliegend behaart
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="117D4E50DF2C02A11B505FFE8E2655A2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
frisch silberig 
<normalizedToken id="DED20D1345384FF21EC59A650BB241E1" originalValue="glänzend" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">glaenzend</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Haare 0,5-1 mm lang). - 
<normalizedToken id="C39490B1EACC5E8535D37EAACFE4FB0C" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4C21064CAE4A7880EA76FACB73EE263A" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
<emphasis id="4AAE449702823993D851D29D8C9CDFEB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="2772452858F68E985F654DEEFEDAA9BA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">12:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="3108341DFAC5CAB54CEA20E9E313C223" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(McCullagh 1934, Delay 1947), aus den 
<normalizedToken id="2ABB137B3EFB9345A8A8C03AD7CE48C0" originalValue="Südwestalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Suedwestalpen</normalizedToken>
(Doulat 1943), aus 
<normalizedToken id="A19F79EA6A3F97E9943D40B6951AC981" originalValue="Rumänien" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Rumaenien</normalizedToken>
(Rahn in 
<normalizedToken id="04AA86AD490F8878913A588C6BA2C9B0" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1966a).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1726BEF8C3187EC19201163F1B89B9DF" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
<emphasis id="18372B0C3B501E58F0CA67E7186A400B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan, seltener subalpin. Trockene, steinige, kalkreiche 
<normalizedToken id="E560B3B68DD300D1C7489B81E1052580" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Grasige 
<normalizedToken id="7119730BE1CAA12328BD97518A8D545B" originalValue="Hänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Haenge</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="2201659A52BADD2E6F83A78A009B38B5" originalValue="Schutthänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Schutthaenge</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="123CAB5DAA125083266364D6C42A89CF" originalValue="Felsbänder" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Felsbaender</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B1F45215FEE33FF0152B65682535F7C6" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
<emphasis id="032474FC16F589789F6420A80BD27AAF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="801957DFD1CA10B1F328ABBE66DC0820" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="C149060DBB346BB67D5CBB693F964485" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">
<normalizedToken id="227CE7B8207C2918B7EAA60342D05DC4" originalValue="südlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">suedlich</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="FA61B2AEA861E394ADAEF697496F9D11" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">:</emphasis>
Lerida (Nordostspanien), 
<normalizedToken id="72FC15847B547C647F36805E0B7865FA" originalValue="Ostpyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Ostpyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="B4A47EA37EC34178CA8BC81CB1ED4900" originalValue="Corbières" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Corbieres</normalizedToken>
, Cevennen, 
<normalizedToken id="E0646AC7035378F817A207246D20884F" originalValue="Südwest-" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Suedwest-</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="4A00B8E88B5AC7C6522B02008E4AED67" originalValue="Südostalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Suedostalpen</normalizedToken>
, Apenninen (
<normalizedToken id="7CFA9B91FC042CF5E8D16B04E49016CA" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Monte Pollino), Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel, mittelungarische Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="DB43E22BA0E9D85B613D8F4746C174FF" originalValue="Siebenbürgen" pageId="null" pageNumber="275">Siebenbuergen</normalizedToken>
. - Im Gebiet: Aostatal (Villefrancbe), Bergamasker Alpen (z.B. Corno Stella, Valle Brembana); sonst selten adventiv.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
